### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">لَهُم مِّن فَوْقِهِمْ ظُلَلٌ مِّنَ ٱلنَّارِ وَمِن تَحْتِهِمْ ظُلَلٌ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ يُخَوِّفُ ٱللَّهُ بِهِۦ عِبَادَهُۥ ۚ يَـٰعِبَادِ فَٱتَّقُونِ</span>

### English

They will have layers of fire above and below them. That is what Allah warns His servants with. So fear Me, O  My servants!